      "set:html": "<p><code dir=\"auto\">session</code> is an object that allows data to be stored between requests for <a href=\"/en/guides/on-demand-rendering/\">routes rendered on demand</a>. It is associated with a cookie that contains the session ID only: the data itself is not stored in the cookie.</p>\n<p>The session is created when first used, and the session cookie is automatically set. The <code dir=\"auto\">session</code> object is <code dir=\"auto\">undefined</code> if no session storage has been configured, or if the current route is prerendered, and will log an error if you try to use it.</p>\n<p>See <a href=\"/en/guides/sessions/\">the session guide</a> for more information on how to use sessions in your Astro project.</p>\n<div class=\"sl-heading-wrapper level-h4\"><h4 id=\"get\"><code dir=\"auto\">get()</code></h4><a class=\"sl-anchor-link\" href=\"#get\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"sl-anchor-icon\"><svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentcolor\" d=\"m12.11 15.39-3.88 3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1-3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0-3.5l3.88-3.88a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-3.88 3.89a4.48 4.48 0 0 0 6.33 6.33l3.89-3.88a1 1 0 1 0-1.42-1.42Zm8.58-12.08a4.49 4.49 0 0 0-6.33 0l-3.89 3.88a1 1 0 0 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1 3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0 3.5l-3.88 3.88a1 1 0 1 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.89a4.49 4.49 0 0 0 0-6.33ZM8.83 15.17a1 1 0 0 0 1.1.22 1 1 0 0 0 .32-.22l4.92-4.92a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-4.92 4.92a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.42Z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"sr-only\">Section titled “get()”</span></a></div>\n<p><p><strong>Type</strong>: <code dir=\"auto\">(key: string) => Promise&#x3C;any></code></p></p>\n<p>Returns the value of the given key in the session. If the key does not exist, it returns <code dir=\"auto\">undefined</code>.</p>\n"
